DataSource.query:
WITH TrickleTable as (
SELECT  '20' + SUBSTRING ( perakt, 1, 2) + SUBSTRING ( perakt, 3, 2) + SUBSTRING ( perakt, 5, 2) + bol as vLine
FROM Production_TRICKLE
WHERE sequenceno > ?pSequence? 
Group by perakt, bol 
),
LoadTable as (
SELECT TRIM ( period ) + actuality +company as vLine2 FROM f_md_FAP
Group by period, actuality, company   
) 
Select TrickleTable.vLine as vResult, 'In trickle table not in load table' as vDesciption from TrickleTable where TrickleTable.vLine NOT IN  ( SELECT LoadTable.vLine2 FROM LoadTable )
UNION
Select LoadTable.vLine2 as vResult, 'In load table not in trickle table' as vDesciption from LoadTable where LoadTable.vLine2 NOT IN  ( SELECT TrickleTable.vLine FROM TrickleTable )
